data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of the coveted Fairhaven Community! This well-maintained and stunning residence boasts a fantastic open floor plan, offering the perfect blend of style and functionality. With 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a spacious bonus loft/flex space, this home provides ample space for comfortable living and entertaining.    Located strategically, this property is a stone's throw away from essential amenities. The proximity to schools, hospitals, and shopping makes daily life a breeze, while the easy access to SH 130 toll road and I-35 ensures convenient travel to nearby destinations.    Nestled in the desirable Fairhaven Community, this home is situated off Westinghouse Road and Rockride Lane, near Williams Elementary School and various parks. The neighborhood exudes a sense of community and tranquility, making it an ideal place to call home.    Residents of Fairhaven enjoy a plethora of community amenities. The community center features a refreshing pool with a kids' splash pad, perfect for warm summer days. The playground, open-air pavilion, walking paths, and pickleball courts offer a variety of recreational options for residents of all ages.    With its ideal location, spacious layout, and access to fantastic community amenities, this home is a rare find. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Fairhaven gem your own! Schedule a showing today and experience the epitome of comfortable and convenient living.
